snippet.title: Judero Trailer 2
snippet.description:
Wishlist now! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1960900/Judero/

By the sea dew and the fall
By the first days of creation.
By the victory of dreams that dinna pass. 
And beside us, angels that hold back deceit. 
I swear by silken hair
That I have rejected that soft, sinful bed. 
I swear by silence and sorrow and truth,
and by the final look of my own eye. 
That ilka sour-headed thought and cantrip
should pass me by. 
Judero, In Dagda's river form, the tale of darkness born of light.
